A vibrant, slightly chaotic Magic: The Gathering art piece depicting a swirling, golden-hued enchantment card titled "Mass Intoxication." Multiple stylized, translucent beer mugs and cocktails explode around a central, ornate, slightly tilted hourglass filled with swirling beer foam.  A single, mischievous imp floats within the hourglass, rolling a six-sided die. Style: slightly whimsical and dynamic, with a touch of magical realism.